display.shortDescription: An early interpretation of DC’s soup profile. Tasty and worth sharing.
display.description: Originally described by DC on EAF Discord. Modern style shot at an ~1:2.5-3 ratio with a very coarse grind, gentle puck saturation, followed by fast water flow (~8-12 sec). Intended for light to wheatgrass roast coffees and results in the cup are similar to filter coffee but with much more intense acidity.
